Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.71,0:00:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,桐生萌郁\N{\fnAPTX柯黑\fs50}桐生萌郁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不許叫！\N{\fnAPTX柯黑\fs50}騒ぐな！
